bilingual.source: The parade was a display of military pomp.
bilingual.target: 游行展示了军事的盛况。

bilingual.source: Scientists are researching invisibility cloaks for military use.
bilingual.target: 科学家们正在研究用于军事的隐形斗篷。

bilingual.source: The state farms were semi-military in character.
bilingual.target: 那些国有农场从性质上讲是半军事的。

bilingual.source: There were special acta of municipal, legal, or military content.
bilingual.target: 内容包括市政、法律、军事的特殊纪闻。

bilingual.source: So a military build-up needs to be accompanied by a build-up of trust.
bilingual.target: 因此，信任的增进需要与军事的加强同时进行。

bilingual.source: China has to catch up with the military advanced level in the world.
bilingual.target: 中国要赶上世界军事的高水平。

bilingual.source: There was a military math facility here just like the one in Madison Wisconsin.
bilingual.target: 这里曾经有军事的数学设备,和Madison，Wisconsin的一样。

bilingual.source: They have the most developed technology, economic and military affairs in the world.
bilingual.target: 他们有最多发展的技术, 在世界上的经济和军事的事件.

bilingual.source: The astronauts had developed a pecking order that was military in its rigidity ( Tom Wolfe )
bilingual.target: 宇航员已经发展成一个严格的军事的特权阶层 ( 汤姆沃尔夫 )

bilingual.source: The coming of knowledge - based military caused the reform in every area of materiel support.
bilingual.target: 知识军事的到来,使装备保障领域的方方面面产生了深刻的变革.

yingyinNormal.en: And then to our own military.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后是我们的军队。

yingyinNormal.en: You are the military emissary to the Great Kublai Khan?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就是忽必烈大汗派来的军事使臣吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This is now a CIA military op. You're indemnified. Respond.
yingyinNormal.zh: 必须采取中情局军事行动，你不必负法律责任，快行动！

yingyinNormal.en: The money's not happening and neither is the military withdrawal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 赎金和撤军都别指望了。

yingyinNormal.en: I was born in Japan, at a military base in Okinawa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我出生在日本冲绳的军事基地。

yingyinNormal.en: My guess is former military with a side of hero complex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜你是退役军人，有点英雄情结。

yingyinNormal.en: It's manned by both military and civilian personnel from District 2.
yingyinNormal.zh: 由第二区的军事和非军事人员共同操作。

yingyinNormal.en: In aerospace, the military, we will own the entire robotics industry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可以应用在航太和军事我们将称霸机器人产业。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a Lycantant, bred for the military, but that didn't work out for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个基因战士，就是为战斗而生的，但现在不再是了。

yingyinNormal.en: The facility is hidden beneath the local power plant under military guard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个设备被藏在本地发电厂的地底，周围有军队守卫。

yingyinNormal.en: What's most alarming is the rate at which their military power is expanding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最令人警惕的是他们的军事扩展速度。

yingyinNormal.en: American military power is unmatched, but this can't be America's fight alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国拥有世界一流的军事力量，但这不应该是美国独自进行的战斗。

yingyinNormal.en: All lines of communication have been compromised, both civilian and military. Shit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有通讯线路都被控制了，不论是军用还是民用。见鬼。

yingyinNormal.en: Rumor is he's got his sights set on Wheeler Lab, the new military think tank at M.I.T.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听说他已经盯上了惠勒实验室，那个在麻省理工的新军事技术中心。

yingyinNormal.en: I found a tattoo shop nearby. It has four stars on Yelp, and it has military discount.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我找到附近的一家纹身店，大众点评上四颗星，军人还享有折扣。

yingyinNormal.en: So who gave prototype military rounds to tuareg fighters in the Sahara? The ask, Lois.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以是谁把军方正在研究的模型给了撒哈拉沙漠里的图阿格雷人？你是记者，你来告诉我。

yingyinNormal.en: District 8. They reported heavy bombing last week. There are no military targets left.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第8区，报道说那里上星期刚被轰炸过，那里已经没有任何军事目标了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's never been tested in the field. Labs, military bases, but not on civilian streets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的原型从没实地演练过，都是在实验室而不是大街上。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is? A tech bomb. Designed to block an entire military communication grid for 24 hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是什么？一种高科技炸弹，可以阻断整个军队的通讯系统长达24小时。

yingyinNormal.en: You are no longer a member of the military. You're unable to attend this meeting. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您不再是军人。你不能参加此审议，我很遗憾。

数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
